name: CryptoMushrooms #001 - Stropharia Aeruginosa
description:
This startling slimy mushroom most know as “Verdigris Agaric” is a rare find, occurring mainly in lawns, woodlands and roadsides from spring to autumn in Britain, Europe, Asia and parts of North America. Most sources claim that it is highly poisonous, although effects are not well known and its toxic constituents undescribed.
